      "blocks": {
        "i1": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "DRINK COFFEE,\\bNOT CALORIES",
            "body": "<p>All flavor, no sugar rush. We use just organic coffee and filtered water, so you get rich, bold taste without the empty calories.</p><p>Strong enough for long days. Smooth enough for easy mornings.</p>",
            "image_side": "auto",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/item-1-drink-coffee.png",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary-gold"
          }
        },
        "i2": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "TASTY FLAVORS,\\bZERO GUILT",
            "body": "<p>From Straight Black to fan-favorite flavors, every sip tastes indulgent - but it's still 100% coffee.</p><p>Tastes decadent, feels energizing, and behaves better than your dessert latte.</p>",
            "image_side": "auto",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/item-2-tasty-flavors.png",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary-gold"
          }
        },
        "i3": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "title": "LIVE LONGER\\bAND HEALTHIER",
            "body": "<p>According to <u>a study of over 170,000 people</u>, those who drank 1.5-3.5 cups of coffee per day were up to 30% less likely to die than those who didn't.</p><p>So feel good about that morning coffee...and better about your second morning coffee...and fantastic about your afternoon coffee. You're going to live forever.</p>",
            "image_side": "auto",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/item-3-live-longer.png",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary-gold"
          }
        }
      },
